rows.label: tev000601_MSG0001
rows.name:
Everything that's ever happened in this wretched world
was all leading up to this one drink. Aaaaaah...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG0002
rows.name: Hey, pal! You come here to raise a glass with ol' Frye?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG0003
rows.name:
The Scotch in this dump ain't so bad, you know?
You should have one. ...Or three.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1001
rows.name: You come here to have another drink with me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1002
rows.name:
What? You're heading off on a mission? Bwa ha ha!
Well sure, go save some lives or whatever.
Heck, I'll come along if you want. Whaddya say?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0011
rows.name: Add Frye to your team.

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0020
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0021
rows.name: Decline Frye's request for now.

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1003
rows.name:
Lemme just pour the rest of my Scotch into my flask...
All right! I'm geared up and ready to go![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1004
rows.name:
What, you don't want me along? Pffft. Your loss.
Just come find me when you change your mind, pal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1009
rows.name:
I wonder what kinda booze these unidentified
xenoforms drink?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1010
rows.name:
Guess if I wanna ask 'em, I gotta save 'em first!
Come on, pal, take me with you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0030
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0031
rows.name: Add Frye to your team.

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0040
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0041
rows.name: Decline Frye's request for now.

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1013
rows.name:
What, you don't want me along? Pffft. Your loss.
Just come find me when you change your mind, pal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1018
rows.name:
Urgh... I've been hitting the Scotch nonstop for the last
couple of days, and I got a hangover like you wouldn't
believe. Feels like I've been chewing tennis balls.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1019
rows.name: It's seriously made my mimeosome go all funky.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1020
rows.name:
Got so much liquor on my breath that even the tainted
would be able to smell me coming a mile away.
Think I'd better take a pass on this mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1025
rows.name:
Sounds like Irina's team hit a rough patch out in
Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1026
rows.name:
They're fellow Interceptors, so I can't just sit here and
drink all day without feeling like I oughta be helping
'em out, ya know? So come on! Take me along![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0050
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0051
rows.name: Add Frye to your team.

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0060
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0061
rows.name: Decline Frye's request for now.

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1028
rows.name:
What, you don't want me along? Pffft. Your loss.
Just come find me when you change your mind, pal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1033
rows.name:
Your next mission's to Sylvalum, huh?
You know, I've been there myself a time or two.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1034
rows.name:
Just gimme a flask and a compass, and I'll find you
that piece of the Lifehold before you can say boo.
Heck, I'll find all the pieces ya want! Whaddya say?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0070
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0071
rows.name: Add Frye to your team.

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0080
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0081
rows.name: Decline Frye's request for now.

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1036
rows.name:
What, you don't want me along? Pffft. Your loss.
Just come find me when you change your mind, pal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1041
rows.name:
Heard Vandham's got another mission for ya.
I dunno what it's gonna take to get that guy off
your back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1042
rows.name:
Here, I'll go with you. We'll find a nice scenic spot
and raise a glass or three to Sylvalum. Whaddya say?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0090
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0091
rows.name: Add Frye to your team.

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0100
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0101
rows.name: Decline Frye's request for now.

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1044
rows.name:
What, you don't want me along? Pffft. Your loss.
Just come find me when you change your mind, pal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1049
rows.name:
Aw, man, I can't believe he made off with that new
Skell AND the Lifehold Core coordinates!
I tell you whatâ€”I did NOT see that coming.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1050
rows.name:
Kinda makes sense when you think about it, though.
Guy was a crackerjack Pathfinder, so it's no surprise
he'd make a good traitor.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1051
rows.name:
Anyway, we gotta go get all that stuff back, and fast.
There's no way in hell I'm letting that little sneak get
the last laugh! So bring me along, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0110
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0111
rows.name: Add Frye to your team.

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0120
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0121
rows.name: Decline Frye's request for now.

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1053
rows.name:
What, you don't want me along? Pffft. Your loss.
Just come find me when you change your mind, pal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1058
rows.name:
I bet Scotch tastes all the better when it's gliding down
the throat of a flesh-and-blood body.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1059
rows.name:
Aw, just the thought gets me tipsy! So come on!
You gotta take me along, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0130
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0131
rows.name: Add Frye to your team.

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0140
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0141
rows.name: Decline Frye's request for now.

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1060
rows.name:
Thanks, [ST:playername ]. It means a lot that
you'd bring me on such an important mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1061
rows.name: Then I'll be drinking to your victory from right here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1066
rows.name:
It's just been one victory party after another here at
the ol' diner.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1067
rows.name:
Needless to say, the booze has been flowing, and I've
had a glass or two. Or 20. ...Or more, maybe?
Anyway, can't say I ain't starting to feel it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1068
rows.name:
Whaddya say, pal? How 'bout you take me with
you so I can get some fresh air?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0150
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0151
rows.name: Add Frye to your team.

rows.label: tev000601_JNK0160
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: tev000601_SEL0161
rows.name: Decline Frye's request for now.

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1069
rows.name:
All right! Let's go bang out a mission or two.
That oughta sober me right up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1070
rows.name:
What, you don't want me along? Pffft. Your loss.
Just come find me when you change your mind, pal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1071
rows.name:
Hey, it's my old pal [ST:playername ]!
Why don'tcha take me along, and... Eh... Never mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000601_MSG1072
rows.name:
I ain't in the mood to fight. I just wanna sit here and
drink my drink. Just enjoy the riches of life and...
whatever else it is I'm doing. Sorry, pal.[ST:wait ]
